{"info": {"author": "", "author_email": "", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": [], "description": "# Python Markdown Auto Direction\n\n[![pypi](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/markdown-autodirection.svg?style=flat)][pypi-url]\n[![](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/markdown-autodirection.svg?style=flat)][license-url]\n[![](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/markdown-autodirection.svg?style=flat)][pypi-url]\n[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/aliva/python-markdown-autodirection.svg?branch=master)][travis-url]\n\n[pypi-url]: https://pypi.org/project/markdown-autodirection/\n[license-url]: LICENSE\n[travis-url]: https://travis-ci.org/aliva/python-markdown-autodirection\n\nAdds `dir=\"auto\"` attribute to paragraphs,\nThis will help browser to set text direction based on the content of current paragraphs\n\n## Install\n\n```\npip install markdown-autodirection\n```\n\n## Use\n\n```python\ntext = \"Text\"\nfrom markdown import markdown\nhtml = markdown(text, extensions=['autodirection'])\nprint(html)\n# <p dir=\"auto\">Text</p>\n```", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/aliva/python-markdown-autodirection/", "keywords": "", "license": "BSD 3-Clause License", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "markdown-autodirection", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/markdown-autodirection/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/markdown-autodirection/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/aliva/python-markdown-autodirection/"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/markdown-autodirection/0.3/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "Extension for markdown package to set paragraph direction to `auto`", "version": "0.3", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>Python Markdown Auto Direction</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/markdown-autodirection/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pypi\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/249b78a55ec72ca91fff0bb38fb7fd1d27ffd938/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f707970692f762f6d61726b646f776e2d6175746f646972656374696f6e2e7376673f7374796c653d666c6174\"></a>\n<a href=\"LICENSE\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/4d5e2d966075b8a1494052cfea699f431d616d17/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f707970692f6c2f6d61726b646f776e2d6175746f646972656374696f6e2e7376673f7374796c653d666c6174\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/markdown-autodirection/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/a52694fb8fb54659d645a89a8203df90a46144b3/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f707970692f646d2f6d61726b646f776e2d6175746f646972656374696f6e2e7376673f7374796c653d666c6174\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/aliva/python-markdown-autodirection\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Build Status\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/e14088b7aa4173cf58dfa3949bdaf65c66d6207c/68747470733a2f2f7472617669732d63692e6f72672f616c6976612f707974686f6e2d6d61726b646f776e2d6175746f646972656374696f6e2e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\"></a></p>\n<p>Adds <code>dir=\"auto\"</code> attribute to paragraphs,\nThis will help browser to set text direction based on the content of current paragraphs</p>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<pre><code>pip install markdown-autodirection\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Use</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"n\">text</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Text\"</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">markdown</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">markdown</span>\n<span class=\"n\">html</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">markdown</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">text</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">extensions</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'autodirection'</span><span class=\"p\">])</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">html</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># &lt;p dir=\"auto\"&gt;Text&lt;/p&gt;</span>\n</pre>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 4825271, "releases": {"0.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "b1c6fea9d6ed45cbcb1e2a329a766c2b", "sha256": "08635d065876a20200e799d4fe4fa6f9e79602171140e0f95be904ce0fd021be"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "markdown-autodirection-0.2.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "b1c6fea9d6ed45cbcb1e2a329a766c2b", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 2369, "upload_time": "2019-02-11T16:32:53", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-02-11T16:32:53.855990Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/b8/af/2d70c0b8f1bee852e7a221b5c4b4c56193ba8d441fd2c6073203806dfa56/markdown-autodirection-0.2.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.2.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "47ccfb2a5cc241fcb0299d71e9d8301d", "sha256": "be7097e57538e377816c7866ef4f1ee4a8fa5c69b205ca11f978381751304fba"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "markdown-autodirection-0.2.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "47ccfb2a5cc241fcb0299d71e9d8301d", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 2389, "upload_time": "2019-02-11T16:34:50", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-02-11T16:34:50.026376Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/72/fb/17eafd60589b96450b17137c497534f8ebc77c2d28c985ea67f0bade786d/markdown-autodirection-0.2.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.3": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "90fc141b5828c9058b4e51a12020d69c", "sha256": "d490be05a7f00420e65d596d0c11752bbf34d04e0f1b35bc3d5e23dd613b1927"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "markdown-autodirection-0.3.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "90fc141b5828c9058b4e51a12020d69c", "packagetype": "sdist", "pyth